            "answer": "<p>When you book, you choose a convenient Northland meetup spot from a list of Kansas City Northland QuikTrip locations. We meet at your scheduled time, we confirm your racquet details, and take it for stringing. Once it's done, we contact you to arrange pickup usually at the same place that you dropped it off.</p>",
